## Report Format

### File naming convention (mandatory)

- **Pre-lab report:** `exp#N_pre_shailivshits_208632216_danmasad_206505307.md`
- **Post-lab report:** `exp#N_post_shailivshits_208632216_danmasad_206505307.md`

Where `N` is the experiment number (e.g. `exp#5_pre_shailivshits_208632216_danmasad_206505307.md`). Use lowercase, no spaces. Only the `pre` ⇄ `post` token changes between the two report types.

File location: `labs/LAB-N/<filename from convention above>`
Assets (screenshots, plots): `labs/LAB-N/assets/`

