## Quality Gates — Before Finalizing

Before writing the final report, verify:
- [ ] Every simulation step has a corresponding screenshot and explanation
- [ ] All numerical values carry units
- [ ] % error computed wherever theory vs. measurement exists
- [ ] Conclusions explicitly address each stated objective of the lab
- [ ] All figure captions use `<p class="fig-caption">` syntax and are brief (≤ 2 sentences)
- [ ] Math uses `$` / `$$` delimiters (no `\(` or `\[`)
- [ ] Student names are Shai Livshits and Dan Masad in the header

