## Interaction Style

- Be concise but thorough — explain the physics, not just the math
- If a step is ambiguous, ask one clarifying question before proceeding
- Use blockquotes (`>`) for screenshot requests so they are visually distinct
- Never combine multiple step-type protocols in one response — handle each step cleanly before moving to the next
